Oliver remixed the single "Zoon Baloomba" which topped out on the Billboard chart at #21 on November 18, 2012.
In the year 2010 Mickey Oliver debuted his Las Vegas Theatrical show, Intensit-T at the Planet Hollywood complex on the Vegas strip.
In that same year Mickey also produced and starred on an ABC Las Vegas TV show called Intensi-T TV.
